detailsSection:
The Microsoft System Center Management Pack for Windows Server DHCP 2016 and above facilitates streamlined monitoring and management of DHCP servers within your network.
Compatible with Windows Server DHCP 2016 and later versions, it enhances visibility into the health and performance of DHCP services, enabling prompt identification and resolution of issues through alert-driven notifications.

This Management Pack is a valuable tool for ensuring the efficient operation of DHCP services, leveraging the robust capabilities of System Center Operations Manager.
